summary = ["In London, where Pinochet has been under arrest in a clinic for the last 10 days, a phalanx of British lawyers argued before the High Court of Justice that the arrest order sent from Spain was illegal because the general, 82, is not a Spanish citizen According to the report Pinochet was informed of the arrest order from two policemen, but is convinced it was a mistake and that he is protected by diplomatic immunity .Last week he said that in exercising his powers under the 1989 Extradition Act, he would consider whether the offenses are of a political character and he would take into account any compassionate circumstances"]